Find a local WordPress community Get Started with WordPress Over 60 million people have chosen WordPress to power the place on the web they call “home” — join the family. Get WordPress News From Our Blog Kia ora! Nestled deep in the Pacific – a small, but vibrant Island bids you welcome. Kia ora from WordPress users, developers, community leaders and friends who all reside; resonate or rejoice in New Zealand. Download & install WordPress with our famous 5-minute installation. Publishing has never been easier. Spend some time reading our documentation, get to know WordPress better every day and start helping others, too.
